  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc8\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan Ambassador to the United States met with US President Biden",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lankan Ambassador to the United States Mahinda Samarasinghe has called on US President Joe Biden.",
        "The meeting is expected to be significant as the United States continues to provide assistance to Sri Lanka, which is in the throes of an economic crisis.",
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Mahinda Samarasinghe briefed President Joe Biden on the current situation in Sri Lanka.",
        "Meanwhile, a delegation comprising US Assistant Secretary of State for the Treasury Robert Cabrot, Assistant Secretary of State for South and Central Asia and Ambassador Kelly Geiterling will visit Sri Lanka.",
        "It is noteworthy that the US delegation will stay in Sri Lanka from the 26th to the 29th to meet with top officials."
      ],
